<text>ModPlug is the name for the series of computer software for creating and playing module files, originally developed by Olivier Lapicque. 
* ModPlug Player, a module player developed in conjunction with the original ModPlug Tracker project and the original &quot;ModPlug&quot; browser plugin
* ModPlug Tracker, now known as OpenMPT
* LibModplug (decoding engine) public domain software for the open source multimedia framework GStreamer</text><links>
