* Lasn, K. (2005) &quot;Design Anarchy&quot;, Vancouver: Adbusters Media Foundation
* Lasn, Kalle (2012) &quot;Meme Wars: The Creative Destruction of Neoclassical Economics&quot;, New York: Seven Stories Press, 

