==Racing==
Arlington&#x27;s live racing season formerly ran from the first Friday in May to the second to last Saturday in September. Since 2001 (up until its final season of 2021) races at Arlington had been announced by John G. Dooley.

The following stakes were held at Arlington in 2019.

Grade I 
* Arlington Million
* Beverly D. Stakes
* Secretariat Stakes

Grade III 
* American Derby
* American St. Leger Stakes
* Arlington Handicap
* Arlington Classic Stakes
* Arlington Matron Stakes
* Chicago Handicap
* Hanshin Cup Stakes
* Modesty Handicap
* Pucker Up Stakes

Listed
* Addison Cammack Memorial
* Arlington-Washington Futurity Stakes
* Arlington-Washington Lassie Stakes
* Hatoof Stakes
* Isaac Murphy Handicap

Former Races

* American 1000 Guineas Stakes
* Arlington Oaks
